        <div class="faq-answer">You get one attempt per day, but you can earn retry attempts by completing certain achievements.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
        <div class="faq-question">How do I change my display name?</div>
        <div class="faq-answer">Go to your Profile (tap your stats card) and edit your display name in the settings.</div>
    </div>

